  "title": "FluxTech",
  "description": "A \"tech\" mod focused around schmovement.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0NNfZeg.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"688\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">FluxTech is a mod that is focused around cool movement! The mod adds concepts and items from various games to achieve said movement. While I have various mechanics and references planned, I would be more than happy to receive suggestions from the community!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Pictures</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tefONMm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" />Some paneling from Portal 2.<br /><br /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7irYMte.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /><br />The gels from portal 2 and also the HPD.<br /><br /><img src=\"blob:https://imgur.com/e270bfe3-b194-4aac-a0d2-e76a81dfdf73\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UEUumvm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></p>\n<p>Player standing on Propulsion Gel with the Gravitrons and Aeroarmor on while holding the HPD.<br /><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s3tB1UC.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" />Player launching themselves with the HPD.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ug1ob8Q.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"626\" />Hardlight bridge</p>\n<p><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UqLoKts.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"626\" /><br /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UqLoKts\" alt=\"\" />Endurium flowing out of a pipe</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Recipes:</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">HPD</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8CUeTQM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Aeroarmor</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eaggZtt.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Slime Coated Netherite Boots<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wdWBJ3P.png\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Gravitrons</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a3wCnBz.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Gel<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AQXSShS.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Propulsion Gel<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7F3NE8T.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Repulsion Gel<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mRsLmWN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Melted Enderpearl<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ii7f3mf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Endurium Bucket<br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Fo7MTgL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Hardlight Bridge Emitter</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WLWtK8R.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"232\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/608088354042544139/766012374754787328/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"84\" /></a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Community:</span><br /><a title=\"My Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/Epf6ffw2da\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.freepnglogos.com/uploads/discord-logo-png/concours-discord-cartes-voeux-fortnite-france-6.png\" width=\"101\" height=\"101\" /></a><a title=\"My YouTube\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyzsPpD0PPB7FQy93Yo6xfQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zIpE3Ub.png\" width=\"105\" height=\"74\" /></a><a title=\"My Twitch\" href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/fusion_flux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://assets.stickpng.com/thumbs/580b57fcd9996e24bc43c540.png\" width=\"106\" height=\"106\" /></a><a title=\"My Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/TheFusionFlux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7WSfFBH.png\" width=\"108\" height=\"81\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;Check out my other mods!</span><br /><a title=\"Supernatural Crops\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/supernatural-crops\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VaK19Ko.png\" alt=\"Supernatural Crops\" width=\"65\" height=\"65\" /></a><a title=\"Origins: Umbrellas\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/origins-umbrellas\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q4FeOQ6.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">If you ask for a forge port ill add your kneecaps to <strong><em>the collec</em><em>tion!~</em></strong></span><img src=\"https://imgur.com/0NNfZeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"Infinity\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/a/GvGaiNl\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n",
